## Platform & Stack

**Platform**: Desktop Menubar App (cross-platform: Mac, Windows, Linux)
**Why**: Needs global hotkeys, clipboard access, file system access

| Layer | Technology | Notes |
|-------|------------|-------|
| Language | Java 17+ | LTS, good tooling |
| UI Framework | JavaFX 21 | Modern, CSS-styleable |
| System Tray | java.awt.SystemTray | Built-in |
| Global Hotkeys | JNativeHook | Cross-platform native hooks |
| Local Storage | SQLite (JDBC) | Lightweight, file-based |
| AI | OpenAI API (GPT-4o-mini) | Research article generation |
| Build | Maven | Standard, well-supported |
| Packaging | jpackage | Bundles JRE, creates installers |

