## Judging Strategy

| Criterion | Weight | Our Approach |
|-----------|--------|--------------|
| Innovation | High | Nothing combines context save + curiosity capture. Novel concept. |
| Execution | High | Focus on core features working flawlessly. Polish > feature count. |
| Design | High | Clean, minimal UI. System tray should feel native. Modern JavaFX CSS. |

