## Feature Priorities

### MVP (Must Ship)
- [ ] System tray icon with menu
- [ ] Global hotkey: Save context (Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+S)
- [ ] Global hotkey: "I wish" (Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+W)
- [ ] Context capture: clipboard, active window title
- [ ] Context restore: show summary popup
- [ ] Wish queue: text input, list view
- [ ] AI research: generate 2-3 paragraph article per wish
- [ ] Settings: API key input

### Nice to Have
- [ ] Voice input for wishes (Java Speech API or cloud)
- [ ] Browser tab capture (requires companion extension)
- [ ] Interrupt analytics
- [ ] Spaced repetition for wishes
- [ ] Export to Obsidian/Notion

### Won't Do (v1)
- [ ] Full browser extension
- [ ] Mobile app
- [ ] Team/sync features

